{"tid":333555,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門人請不要忘記吳明欽","createTime":"2017-07-24T02:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T08:04:59.000Z","uid":8543,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb30f138e51daa396b3d0e6c77ec3907be1a834","tid":333555,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:05:26.000Z","msg":"吳明欽（1955年4月13日－1992年6月22日），曾經是「三料議員」，集區議員、區域市政局議員、香港立法局議員於一身，亦是香港首位遇襲的區議員。1985年夥拍同為匯點成員的朱偉彬參選屯門區議會大興選區，並擊敗尋求連任的鄉事人士聶澤棠當選，他並獲得四千七百票成為區選票王，至今紀錄保持近三十年仍未被打破；1986年開始出任區域市政局議員；1989年當選為香港十大傑出青年。1991年他聯同黃偉賢在新界西參選香港立法局選舉，最後吳明欽以高票當選，黃偉賢則敗於戴展華之下，吳明欽成為香港首批民主派立法局直選議員。 <br />\n<br />\n吳明欽原為中學教師，曾任教佛教沈香林紀念中學，當時與民主黨前主席李永達為同事。當選區議員不久的1985年10月11日於大興邨遭3名手持水喉鐵的男子襲擊受傷，懷疑與地區糾紛有關。 <br />\n<br />\n吳明欽植根屯門，七次參選各級選舉皆獲勝。然而，1992年2月發現患上血癌，被送到瑪麗醫院進行骨髓移植手術，但出現併發症，於同年6月22日病逝，享年37歲。港同盟派何俊仁爭奪吳明欽逝世後遺留下來的立法局議席，但敗於鄉事派候選人鄧兆棠。"},{"pid":"318d0595a2be6c64d456c8d53820c1be9b808617","tid":333555,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77944d41e78db02bbb8b294a25809754d4deb278","tid":333555,"uid":9017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"當年佢幫過我屋企人<br />\n佢行左真係唔開心"},{"pid":"b5e7aa825278e0f1a68e3fcfd5139acde0bfc5ea","tid":333555,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"呢度啲會員應該多數未聽過佢個名"},{"pid":"aebb850a1901184f693cb8022c0d83f15c625c8c","tid":333555,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:34:42.000Z","msg":"37就走"},{"pid":"30cacfb62e07728e3ac98cdfcccc7d0371163935","tid":333555,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:52:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年佢幫過我屋企人<br />\n佢行左真係唔開心</blockquote><br />\n佢同我屋企人都好有關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e657d7832f2db7f88e8af39bef99e8625ff6f8f","tid":333555,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:53:37.000Z","msg":"港同盟係民主黨前身（另一合併組織為「匯點」）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57b4dff3b5837180ad0f188ea5e9c7486471711","tid":333555,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港同盟係民主黨前身（另一合併組織為「匯點」）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢同班泛民冇得比"},{"pid":"214eb5a3c2377f65141ce3bff81fa22390a76273","tid":333555,"uid":90863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:55:17.000Z","msg":"活到今日咪又係比連登仔屌佢飯民鳩做"},{"pid":"889ef1d2d1b678ccc64162c6c7df01dbd2b51ab2","tid":333555,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"係佢令我知道，原來選民手上的一票係可以有咁大嘅力量。<br />\n<br />\n以前大興人，當時我仲係細路，當時對佢嘅離開已經感到好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9445b594fb5993e45b0a454f62990594280cf162","tid":333555,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a04702889e9c63d2752a1b09ba628677377f01b","tid":333555,"uid":42767,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:26:14.000Z","msg":"八十年代，劉皇發旗下的屯門鄉事想在新墟自己酒樓門口，強行更改班馬線安排於是拿著50萬，想收買吳明欽 (差吳明欽一票就通過)。你估自小窮困嘅吳明欽先生怎回答?<br />\n<br />\n「你畀五億都買唔到我！」<br />\n<br />\n幾日後，議案不能通過，吳明欽就被人用水喉鐵圍劈，身體越來越差。1992年血癌病逝。<br />\n<br />\n1985年，屯門景峰兩房單位才賣17萬，50萬即係三層樓。今日若有人拎三層樓收買議員改班馬線，有幾多人會拒絕？<br />\n<br />\n為一條班馬線就劈人，狂劈當年新西以至全港最好的議員<br />\n<br />\n這就是鄉事派，這就是劉皇發。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/conradwu/posts/10155644387750774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fconradwu%2Fposts%2F10155644387750774&d=XYhUiEuAbtPYRjPsqohspuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=30c6755b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/conradwu/posts/10155644387750774</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n響膠登見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73036ca1d70f211500a42be58cdeaa9ffebe1fe4","tid":333555,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:27:46.000Z","msg":"啲屯門人話係人都知佢畀死去的人賄賂<br />\n開價五十萬都唔要<br />\n之後畀人持械圍毆"},{"pid":"bdcbc44d0c994f35cecb926aa3ef6bf108549193","tid":333555,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:30:14.000Z","msg":"1985年10月11日晚，匯點屯門區議員票王吳明欽在該區工作時，遭人用水喉鐵及利刀襲擊傷重送院，至19日出院。吳氏多次強調並非私怨，相信事件與公務有關。有傳是鄉事派要求將該區一條斑馬線改畫到某酒樓門口，動議只差一票通過，有人向吳明欽提出用五十萬元買票，吳拒絕，數天後就遇擊。<br />\n<br />\n其後警方拘捕五名青年男子，經認人後四人提堂。最後兩人獲釋，兩人判入勞役中心半年。律政司上訴後，分別改判入教導所九個月及三年。法官表示，無法查明案件動機及幕後主謀。"},{"pid":"d58a1bcdcc8bd341b9d98f4d30dd3dca370fd851","tid":333555,"uid":54876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:30:52.000Z","msg":"細個淨係記得91直選，讀緊小學，個校長同學生講叫父母投鄧兆棠戴展華，大個先知呢啲就係鄉事派嘅仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855192da05509118a4316ee601afc07322caa13e","tid":333555,"uid":39141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:51:03.000Z","msg":"細個時聽大人講,<br />\n吳明欽痛恨黑社會(新技安)<br />\n原來仲同鄉下佬有牙齒印,<br />\n官商鄉黑, 合作無間幾十年!!!"},{"pid":"abece3a202e797862b7f6db200c9cec8f88c0a30","tid":333555,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲屯門人話係人都知佢畀<span style=\"color: red;\">死去的人</span>賄賂<br />\n開價五十萬都唔要<br />\n之後畀人持械圍毆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n某位剛死去的人.........."},{"pid":"3ac32864faf7f3ae3b5ab44b2dc628128b9241ab","tid":333555,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:27:24.000Z","msg":"吳sir <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> \\l/"},{"pid":"3d93ba7922875611759ed3c1bedd10ae5a8f630b","tid":333555,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746fb4a041338ff09bd45f5ee54352f039e5892a","tid":333555,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:25:31.000Z","msg":"英年早逝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢死嗰時都未出世未入屯門..但呢種咁熱心嘅議員依家買少見少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df51cf52f518c4850abdf153a20da929b8a1f40a","tid":333555,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:48:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個時聽大人講,<br />\n吳明欽痛恨黑社會(新技安)<br />\n原來仲同鄉下佬有牙齒印,<br />\n官商鄉黑, 合作無間幾十年!!!</blockquote><br />\n咁樣嘅議員真係1001個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566b27344db72f257e4a567394cb6acfdd9124a8","tid":333555,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T18:12:18.000Z","msg":"可惜有能力既唔做 無能力既搶住做就係而家既香港<br />\n有能力又搶住做既 = 找死"},{"pid":"07ac10d6eb17758c94311df4bd7a30a29c591da5","tid":333555,"uid":36157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T18:20:55.000Z","msg":"一個好人咁早走<br />\n另一個冚家剷今時今日先死<br />\n<br />\n乜野叫報應？<br />\n宜家死左要還？<br />\n哂氣啦！"},{"pid":"1fe98d9a8697790d5b22643185575bcc18d93fd6","tid":333555,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T19:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45df559ea83d02e5c46a55be1563fbbdd9dad720","tid":333555,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T20:23:26.000Z","msg":"幾似朱凱迪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係高票當選, 又係俾牛屎佬/黑幫要脅"}]}